version_description: Similar to other versions, but more accurate (accurate chords)

This tab is in the original key of Eb Major. This tab includes many transition chords which are true to the original song, which is played on piano. These chords and quick chord changes make this tab 'Advanced' rather than intermediate. Song corresponds to Warner Live Room and original recording of the song.
No finger picking. Different chords on the bridge.

Chords for piano mainly, there are important Ab Cm/G Fm chord where there is crucial to play bass descending sequence A G F to make it sound right, in chorus it's very important to play ascending melodic notes ( chord highest notes ) Bb, C, Db, Eb on last four chords to keep the feel of tension and right melody of the song ( listen to it to understand what I mean ), enjoy this beautiful song.
